1962;;Fate Takes a Hand;;British;;Max Varnel;;Ronald Howard, Christina Gregg;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fate_Takes_a_Hand;;The recovery of a mail bag stolen in a robbery 15 years before has varying consequences on the lives of five of the recipients of the letters, when the post office decide that the mail should be delivered. Several lives are changed, as witnessed by a newspaper reporter, accompanied by a post office security officer, who decide to follow up on several of the letters.